name: Youtube Citer
description: This web application cites a youtube video for a bibliography in MLA, APA, Harvard, and Chicago formats.

name: Prince George's County Crime Incidents Visualization
description: This project uses the Prince George's County Open Data API to access the Crime Incidents February 2017 to Present Dataset to see a pattern of crime in Prince George's County and predict if crime will occur in the future.

name: UMD Course Department Comparison
description: This project uses the RESTful UMD API to gather undergraduate course information on UMD course departments. This implements a Graphical User Interface to select two departments and compares the number of level 100, 200, 300 and 400 level courses in bar graphs.

name: Muan Barber Shop
description: A web design concept for a local barber shop in my neighborhood. Designed in Adobe XD
